# ~/.mbsyncrc

IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User mattpatchava@posteo.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --decrypt ~/.mail-passwd.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX

Channel posteo
Far   :posteo-remote:
Near  :posteo-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
